    ],
    "label": "Figure",
    "content": "<img alt=\"Flowchart illustrating the Hazard Identification and Risk Assessment process (5 steps): 1. Hazard Identification (危害風險鑑別), 2. Hazard Identification Details (包括職業災害, 法令規章修正, 作業程序變更, 新增設備, 相關者回饋), 3. Risk Assessment (可接受風險, 不可接受風險), 4. Risk Assessment Details (嚴重性評估, 發生機率分析), 5. Decision on Control Measures (決定控制措施).\"/>",
    "bbox_pdf": [
