    "content": "<img alt=\"Flowchart illustrating the Change Management process: Change required (涉及人員、機械設備、物料、方法、環境等變更, 範疇需進行變更管理) leads to Review Unit Initiation (審查單位發起通知). This leads to Review Unit Content (審查單位審查內容). Review Unit Content leads to two paths: 1. Review Unit Confirmation (審查單位佐證確認), which leads to Change Management Review Passed (變更管理審查通過結案). 2. Review Unit Review (權責單位回覆變更內容及提供佐證資料), which leads back to Review Unit Content.\"/>",
